Build-Depends: dpkg-dev (>= 1.15.7), debhelper (>= 7), libbsd-dev, libedit-dev,
 libc0.1-dev (>= 2.10.1) [kfreebsd-any]
Vcs-Browser: http://svn.debian.org/wsvn/glibc-bsd/trunk/ufsutils/
